    "\"Paying by the year beats paying by the month.\"": {
      "comment": "Number-free yearly plan pitch (testimonial), shown when a storefront-specific saving percentage is unavailable.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"Paying by the year beats paying by the month.\""
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "„Jährlich zahlen ist günstiger als monatlich.“"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "«Pagar por año sale mejor que pagar por mes.»"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "« Payer à l’année revient moins cher qu’au mois. »"
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "«Pagare all’anno conviene più che pagare al mese.»"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "「月払いより年払いのほうがお得です。」"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "“월 결제보다 연 결제가 더 이득이에요.”"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "“Pagar por ano compensa mais do que pagar por mês.”"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "「按年付款比按月付款更划算。」"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "「按年付款比按月付款更划算。」"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "\"Transport\" is how the lookup travels. IP is unencrypted; DoH, DoT, and DoQ scramble it so others on your network can't see the sites you visit.": {
      "comment": "DNS Transport section footer explaining what the transport options mean.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "„Transport“ ist der Weg, den die Abfrage nimmt. IP ist unverschlüsselt; DoH, DoT und DoQ verschlüsseln sie, damit andere in deinem Netzwerk nicht sehen, welche Seiten du besuchst."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"Transport\" is how the lookup travels. IP is unencrypted; DoH, DoT, and DoQ encrypt it so others on your network can't see the sites you visit."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "El «transporte» es cómo viaja la consulta. IP va sin cifrar; DoH, DoT y DoQ la cifran para que nadie más en tu red vea los sitios que visitas."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Le « transport » est la façon dont la requête circule. L'IP n'est pas chiffrée ; DoH, DoT et DoQ la chiffrent pour que personne sur votre réseau ne voie les sites que vous visitez."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Il «trasporto» è il modo in cui viaggia la richiesta. L'IP non è cifrato; DoH, DoT e DoQ lo cifrano, così chi è sulla tua rete non può vedere i siti che visiti."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "「Transport」は問い合わせの送られ方です。IP は暗号化なし。DoH・DoT・DoQ は暗号化するので、同じネットワークの人に訪問先を見られません。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "「Transport」는 조회가 오가는 방식이에요. IP는 암호화되지 않아요. DoH, DoT, DoQ는 조회를 암호화해서 같은 네트워크의 다른 사람이 방문 사이트를 못 보게 해요."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"Transport\" é como a consulta viaja. O IP fica sem criptografia; DoH, DoT e DoQ a embaralham para que outros na sua rede não vejam os sites que você visita."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "「传输方式」指查询如何传送。IP 不加密；DoH、DoT 和 DoQ 会对其加密，让同一网络上的其他人看不到你访问了哪些网站。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "「Transport」是查詢的傳送方式。IP 未加密；DoH、DoT、DoQ 會加密，讓同網路的人看不到你造訪的網站。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "\"We already saved this by unplugging appliances.\"": {
      "comment": "Jokey plan pitch (testimonial) on the upgrade screen.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"We already saved this by unplugging appliances.\""
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "„Das haben wir schon gespart, indem wir Geräte ausgesteckt haben.“"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "«Ya lo ahorramos desenchufando electrodomésticos.»"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "« On a déjà économisé ça en débranchant les appareils. »"
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "«L’abbiamo già risparmiato staccando gli elettrodomestici.»"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "「家電のコンセントを抜いて、これくらいはもう節約済みです。」"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "“가전 플러그를 뽑아서 이 정도는 이미 아꼈어요.”"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "“A gente já economizou isso desligando aparelhos da tomada.”"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "「拔掉电器插头，我们早就省下这笔钱了。」"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "「拔掉電器插頭，我們早就省下這筆錢了。」"
          }
        }
      }
    },
