    "A Lava a day keeps bad domains away.": {
      "comment": "GuardianShieldStyle.settingsDescription .original (SettingsView:2110); shown as Guard-look subtitle when revealed, SettingsView:1976. Catalog-only.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
