    "Add it as a new filter, or replace one of yours. Your allowed exceptions and DNS choice stay put.": {
      "comment": "Localization-gap backfill (wrapper-localized; was hardcoded in ShareableFiltersUI.swift).",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Add it as a new filter, or replace one of yours. Your allowed exceptions and DNS choice stay put."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Füge ihn als neuen Filter hinzu oder ersetze einen deiner Filter. Deine erlaubten Ausnahmen und deine DNS-Wahl bleiben unverändert."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Añádelo como un nuevo filter o reemplaza uno de los tuyos. Tus excepciones permitidas y tu DNS no cambian."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ajoutez-le comme nouveau filtre ou remplacez l'un des vôtres. Vos exceptions autorisées et votre choix de DNS restent inchangés."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Aggiungilo come nuovo filtro o sostituiscine uno tuo. Le eccezioni consentite e la scelta del DNS restano invariate."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "新しいフィルターとして追加するか、既存のフィルターと置き換えます。許可した例外と DNS の選択はそのまま残ります。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "새 필터로 추가하거나 기존 필터를 교체하세요. 허용 예외와 DNS 선택은 그대로 유지돼요."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Adicione como um novo filtro ou substitua um dos seus. Suas exceções permitidas e a escolha de DNS permanecem."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "可将它添加为新筛选器，或替换你现有的某个筛选器。你的放行例外和 DNS 选择保持不变。"
