    "Delete online backup copy removes the server copy but keeps backups on. Turn off & delete backup stops them too. Either way, it's gone for good.": {
      "comment": "Account & Backup: caveat under the two destructive backup options, disambiguating 'Delete online backup copy' (keeps backup on this device) from 'Turn off & delete backup' (stops backups too).",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "„Online-Backup-Kopie löschen“ entfernt die Server-Kopie, lässt Backups aber an. „Backup ausschalten und löschen“ stoppt sie ganz. So oder so ist sie weg."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Delete online backup copy removes the server copy but keeps backups on. Turn off & delete backup stops them too. Either way, it's gone for good."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "«Eliminar la copia en línea» borra la copia del servidor, pero mantiene las copias activas. «Desactivar y eliminar» también las detiene. En ambos casos, se pierde para siempre."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "« Supprimer la copie en ligne » retire la copie du serveur mais garde la sauvegarde active. « Désactiver et supprimer » l'arrête aussi. Dans les deux cas, c'est définitif."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "«Elimina la copia online» rimuove la copia sul server ma lascia attivo il backup. «Disattiva ed elimina» ferma anche quello. In ogni caso, è persa per sempre."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "「オンラインバックアップのコピーを削除」はサーバー上のコピーだけ消し、バックアップは続きます。「バックアップをオフにして削除」は両方止めます。どちらも元に戻せません。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "「온라인 백업 사본 삭제」는 서버 사본만 지우고 백업은 켜 둡니다. 「백업 끄고 삭제」는 백업도 멈춥니다. 어느 쪽이든 영구히 사라집니다."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"Excluir cópia de backup on-line\" apaga a cópia do servidor, mas mantém o backup ativo. \"Desativar e excluir backup\" também para tudo. Nos dois casos, é para sempre."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "“删除在线备份副本”只删除服务器上的副本，备份仍保持开启；“关闭并删除备份”会一并停止。无论哪种，都无法找回。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "「刪除線上備份副本」只刪除伺服器上的副本，備份仍保持開啟；「關閉並刪除備份」會一併停止。無論哪一種，都無法復原。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
