          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Capisco che Lava non può recuperare nessuno dei due."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "I understand that if I lose every unlock method, I may not be able to restore my backup": {
      "comment": "Localization-gap backfill (wrapper-localized; was hardcoded in BackupSetupView.swift).",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "I understand that if I lose every unlock method, I may not be able to restore my backup"
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Mir ist klar: Wenn ich alle Entsperrmethoden verliere, kann ich mein Backup womöglich nicht wiederherstellen"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Entiendo que si pierdo todos los métodos de desbloqueo, quizá no pueda restaurar mi copia de seguridad"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Je comprends que si je perds toutes mes méthodes de déverrouillage, je risque de ne plus pouvoir restaurer ma sauvegarde"
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Capisco che se perdo tutti i metodi di sblocco potrei non riuscire a ripristinare il backup"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "すべてのロック解除方法を失った場合、バックアップを復元できなくなることがあると理解しています"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "모든 잠금 해제 방법을 잃으면 백업을 복원하지 못할 수 있다는 점을 이해해요"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Entendo que, se eu perder todos os métodos de desbloqueio, talvez não consiga restaurar meu backup"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我了解，如果丢失所有解锁方式，可能将无法恢复备份"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我了解若失去所有解鎖方式，可能就無法復原備份"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "IP uses standard DNS. DNS over HTTPS (DoH), TLS (DoT), and QUIC (DoQ) encrypt allowed lookups to the resolver.": {
      "comment": "Detail under the DNS Transport segmented control.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "IP uses standard DNS. DNS over HTTPS (DoH), TLS (DoT), and QUIC (DoQ) encrypt allowed lookups to the resolver."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "IP nutzt Standard-DNS. DNS over HTTPS (DoH), TLS (DoT) und QUIC (DoQ) verschlüsseln erlaubte Anfragen an den Resolver."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "IP usa DNS estándar. DNS sobre HTTPS (DoH), TLS (DoT) y QUIC (DoQ) cifran las consultas permitidas hacia el resolver."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "L'IP utilise le DNS standard. DNS over HTTPS (DoH), TLS (DoT) et QUIC (DoQ) chiffrent les requêtes autorisées vers le résolveur."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "IP usa il DNS standard. DNS over HTTPS (DoH), TLS (DoT) e QUIC (DoQ) cifrano le ricerche consentite verso il resolver."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "IP は標準の DNS を使います。DNS over HTTPS（DoH）、TLS（DoT）、QUIC（DoQ）は、リゾルバへの許可された名前解決を暗号化します。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "IP는 표준 DNS를 사용합니다. DNS over HTTPS(DoH), TLS(DoT), QUIC(DoQ)는 리졸버로 가는 허용된 조회를 암호화합니다."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "O IP usa DNS padrão. DNS sobre HTTPS (DoH), TLS (DoT) e QUIC (DoQ) criptografam as consultas permitidas até o resolvedor."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "IP 使用标准 DNS。DNS over HTTPS (DoH)、TLS (DoT) 和 QUIC (DoQ) 会加密发往解析器的放行查询。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "IP 使用標準 DNS。DNS over HTTPS（DoH）、TLS（DoT）和 QUIC（DoQ）會加密傳送到解析器的允許查詢。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
