    "Monthly and yearly plans auto-renew. Payment is charged to your Apple Account at purchase and renews unless turned off at least 24 hours before the period ends. Manage or cancel in Apple Account settings.": {
      "comment": "Paywall auto-renew disclosure shown when the yearly-paid-monthly plan is NOT offered (omits the 12-month commitment sentence). The with-commitment variant is the longer sibling string.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Monthly and yearly plans auto-renew. Payment is charged to your Apple Account at purchase and renews unless turned off at least 24 hours before the period ends. Manage or cancel in Apple Account settings."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Monats- und Jahresabos verlängern sich automatisch. Der Betrag wird beim Kauf über dein Apple-Konto abgebucht und verlängert sich, sofern du nicht mindestens 24 Stunden vor Periodenende deaktivierst. Verwalten oder kündigen in den Apple-Konto-Einstellungen."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Las suscripciones mensual y anual se renuevan automáticamente. El pago se carga en tu Cuenta de Apple al comprar y se renueva salvo que se desactive al menos 24 horas antes de que termine el periodo. Gestiona o cancela en los ajustes de tu Cuenta de Apple."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Les abonnements mensuel et annuel se renouvellent automatiquement. Le paiement est prélevé sur votre compte Apple à l'achat et se renouvelle sauf désactivation au moins 24 heures avant la fin de la période. Gérez ou résiliez dans les réglages de votre compte Apple."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Gli abbonamenti mensile e annuale si rinnovano automaticamente. Il pagamento è addebitato sull'Account Apple all'acquisto e si rinnova salvo disattivazione almeno 24 ore prima della fine del periodo. Gestisci o annulla nelle impostazioni dell'Account Apple."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "月額と年額は自動更新サブスクリプションです。料金は購入時にAppleアカウントへ請求され、期間終了の24時間以上前にオフにしない限り自動更新されます。管理・解約はAppleアカウント設定で行えます。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "월간 및 연간 구독은 자동 갱신됩니다. 결제는 구입 시 Apple 계정으로 청구되고, 기간 종료 24시간 전까지 끄지 않으면 자동 갱신됩니다. Apple 계정 설정에서 관리하거나 해지하세요."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "As assinaturas mensal e anual são renovadas automaticamente. A cobrança é feita na sua Conta Apple na compra e renova, a menos que seja desativada pelo menos 24 horas antes do fim do período. Gerencie ou cancele nos ajustes da Conta Apple."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "月度和年度订阅会自动续期。购买时从你的 Apple 账户扣款，除非在周期结束前至少 24 小时关闭，否则自动续期。可在 Apple 账户设置中管理或取消。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "月繳與年繳訂閱會自動續訂。購買時向你的 Apple 帳號收費，除非在期間結束前至少 24 小時關閉，否則自動續訂。可在 Apple 帳號設定中管理或取消。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Monthly and yearly plans auto-renew. Yearly paid monthly is billed monthly on a 12-month commitment; after that, cancelling affects the next renewal per App Store terms. Payment is charged to your Apple Account at purchase and renews unless turned off at least 24 hours before the period ends. Manage or cancel in Apple Account settings.": {
      "comment": "Localization-gap backfill (was hardcoded in SettingsView.swift).",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Monthly and yearly plans auto-renew. Yearly paid monthly is billed monthly on a 12-month commitment; after that, cancelling affects the next renewal per App Store terms. Payment is charged to your Apple Account at purchase and renews unless turned off at least 24 hours before the period ends. Manage or cancel in Apple Account settings."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Monats- und Jahresabos verlängern sich automatisch. Jährlich, monatlich bezahlt wird monatlich mit 12-monatiger Verpflichtung abgerechnet; danach wirkt sich eine Kündigung gemäß App Store-Bedingungen auf die nächste Verlängerung aus. Der Betrag wird beim Kauf über dein Apple-Konto abgebucht und verlängert sich, sofern du nicht mindestens 24 Stunden vor Periodenende deaktivierst. Verwalten oder kündigen in den Apple-Konto-Einstellungen."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Las suscripciones mensual y anual se renuevan automáticamente. La anual pagada mensualmente se cobra cada mes con un compromiso de 12 meses; después, cancelar afecta la siguiente renovación según los términos del App Store. El pago se carga en tu Cuenta de Apple al comprar y se renueva salvo que se desactive al menos 24 horas antes de que termine el periodo. Gestiona o cancela en los ajustes de tu Cuenta de Apple."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Les abonnements mensuel et annuel se renouvellent automatiquement. L'annuel payé mensuellement est facturé chaque mois avec un engagement de 12 mois ; ensuite, la résiliation affecte le renouvellement suivant selon les conditions de l'App Store. Le paiement est prélevé sur votre compte Apple à l'achat et se renouvelle sauf désactivation au moins 24 heures avant la fin de la période. Gérez ou résiliez dans les réglages de votre compte Apple."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Gli abbonamenti mensile e annuale si rinnovano automaticamente. L'annuale pagato mensilmente è addebitato ogni mese con un impegno di 12 mesi; poi l'annullamento influisce sul rinnovo successivo secondo i termini dell'App Store. Il pagamento è addebitato sull'Account Apple all'acquisto e si rinnova salvo disattivazione almeno 24 ore prima della fine del periodo. Gestisci o annulla nelle impostazioni dell'Account Apple."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "月額と年額は自動更新サブスクリプションです。「年額（月払い）」は12か月契約として毎月請求され、以降の解約はApp Storeの条件に従い次回の更新に適用されます。料金は購入時にAppleアカウントへ請求され、期間終了の24時間以上前にオフにしない限り自動更新されます。管理・解約はAppleアカウント設定で行えます。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "월간 및 연간 구독은 자동 갱신됩니다. 연간 월별 결제는 12개월 약정으로 매월 청구되며, 이후 해지는 App Store 약관에 따라 다음 갱신에 적용됩니다. 결제는 구입 시 Apple 계정으로 청구되고, 기간 종료 24시간 전까지 끄지 않으면 자동 갱신됩니다. Apple 계정 설정에서 관리하거나 해지하세요."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "As assinaturas mensal e anual são renovadas automaticamente. A anual paga mensalmente é cobrada todo mês com compromisso de 12 meses; depois, cancelar afeta a próxima renovação conforme os termos da App Store. A cobrança é feita na sua Conta Apple na compra e renova, a menos que seja desativada pelo menos 24 horas antes do fim do período. Gerencie ou cancele nos ajustes da Conta Apple."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "月度和年度订阅会自动续期。“年度（按月支付）”按月收费，含 12 个月承诺；之后取消将按 App Store 条款影响下次续期。购买时从你的 Apple 账户扣款，除非在周期结束前至少 24 小时关闭，否则自动续期。可在 Apple 账户设置中管理或取消。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "月繳與年繳訂閱會自動續訂。「年繳（按月支付）」按月收費，含 12 個月承諾；之後取消將依 App Store 條款影響下次續訂。購買時向你的 Apple 帳號收費，除非在期間結束前至少 24 小時關閉，否則自動續訂。可在 Apple 帳號設定中管理或取消。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
