    "Permanently deletes your account's encrypted backup — this can't be undone. Backup stays on, and a fresh copy uploads next time.": {
      "comment": "Localization gap backfill (render-path round 3).",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Permanently deletes your account's encrypted backup — this can't be undone. Backup stays on, and a fresh copy uploads next time."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Löscht das verschlüsselte Backup deines Accounts dauerhaft – nicht rückgängig zu machen. Backup bleibt an und lädt beim nächsten Mal eine neue Kopie hoch."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Elimina de forma permanente la copia cifrada de tu cuenta; no se puede deshacer. La copia sigue activada y subirá una nueva la próxima vez."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Supprime définitivement la sauvegarde chiffrée de votre compte — action irréversible. La sauvegarde reste activée et enverra une nouvelle copie la prochaine fois."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Elimina definitivamente il backup cifrato del tuo account: non è reversibile. Il backup resta attivo e caricherà una nuova copia la prossima volta."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "アカウントの暗号化バックアップを完全に削除します（元に戻せません）。バックアップはオンのままで、次回新しいコピーをアップロードします。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "계정의 암호화된 백업을 영구적으로 삭제합니다. 되돌릴 수 없습니다. 백업은 켜진 채로 유지되며 다음번에 새 사본을 올립니다."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Apaga permanentemente o backup criptografado da sua conta — não dá para desfazer. O backup continua ativado e envia uma nova cópia na próxima vez."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "永久删除你账户的加密备份，无法撤销。备份仍保持开启，下次会上传一份新副本。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "永久刪除你帳號的加密備份，無法復原。備份仍保持開啟，下次會上傳一份新副本。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
