    "This replaces your blocklists and blocked domains. Your allowed exceptions and DNS choice stay put.": {
      "comment": "Footer caution on the import screen. Keep 'DNS' untranslated; 'blocklists'/'blocked domains'/'allowed exceptions' match catalog.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
