    "When your phone can't reach the internet, Lava blocks sites to stay safe — they load again once your connection is back.": {
      "comment": "Filters overview caption shown for the 'Poor' connection preview — explains fail-closed blocking in plain terms. Framed as the PHONE's connectivity (can't reach the internet), NOT 'Lava can't reach its filter' (the filter is local).",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "When your phone can't reach the internet, Lava blocks sites to stay safe — they load again once your connection is back."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Wenn dein Telefon das Internet nicht erreicht, blockiert Lava Websites zur Sicherheit – sie laden wieder, sobald deine Verbindung zurück ist."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cuando tu teléfono no llega a internet, Lava bloquea los sitios para protegerte; vuelven a cargar cuando tu conexión regresa."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Quand ton téléphone n'atteint pas Internet, Lava bloque les sites par sécurité — ils se rechargent dès que ta connexion revient."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Quando il telefono non raggiunge Internet, Lava blocca i siti per sicurezza: si ricaricano appena torna la connessione."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "スマホがインターネットに接続できないときは、安全のため Lava がサイトをブロックします。接続が戻れば再び読み込めます。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "휴대폰이 인터넷에 연결되지 않으면 Lava가 안전을 위해 사이트를 차단합니다. 연결이 복구되면 다시 열립니다."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Quando o seu telefone não alcança a internet, o Lava bloqueia os sites por segurança — eles voltam a carregar quando a conexão volta."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "当手机无法连接互联网时，Lava 会拦截网站以保护你；网络恢复后会重新加载。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "當手機無法連上網際網路時，Lava 會攔截網站以保護你；連線恢復後會重新載入。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
